sql_query.sql:
SELECT COUNT(*) FROM (SELECT 1 AS one FROM "categories" WHERE ((FALSE AND LENGTH(COALESCE(email_in, '')) > 0 AND email_in_allow_strangers)
          OR categories.id NOT IN (SELECT category_id FROM category_groups)
          OR categories.id IN (
                SELECT category_id
                  FROM category_groups
                 WHERE permission_type IN (1)
                   AND (group_id = 0 OR group_id IN (SELECT group_id FROM group_users WHERE user_id = 186))
             )) LIMIT 1) subquery_for_count

sql_query.sql:
SELECT COUNT(*) FROM "categories" WHERE ((FALSE AND LENGTH(COALESCE(email_in, '')) > 0 AND email_in_allow_strangers)
          OR categories.id NOT IN (SELECT category_id FROM category_groups)
          OR categories.id IN (
                SELECT category_id
                  FROM category_groups
                 WHERE permission_type IN (1)
                   AND (group_id = 0 OR group_id IN (SELECT group_id FROM group_users WHERE user_id = 186))
             )) AND "categories"."id" = 77
SELECT "category_custom_fields"."name", "category_custom_fields"."value" FROM "category_custom_fields" WHERE "category_custom_fields"."category_id" = 77 ORDER BY id asc
SELECT "tags"."name" FROM "tags" INNER JOIN "topic_tags" ON "tags"."id" = "topic_tags"."tag_id" WHERE "topic_tags"."topic_id" = 283
SELECT COUNT(*) FROM "tags" INNER JOIN "category_tags" ON "tags"."id" = "category_tags"."tag_id" WHERE "category_tags"."category_id" = 77

SELECT "tags"."name" FROM "tags" INNER JOIN "tag_group_memberships" ON "tag_group_memberships"."tag_id" = "tags"."id" INNER JOIN "tag_groups" ON "tag_groups"."id" = "tag_group_memberships"."tag_group_id" WHERE (tag_groups.id NOT IN (
        SELECT tag_group_id
        FROM tag_group_permissions
        WHERE group_id = 0))

SELECT "tags"."name" FROM "tags" INNER JOIN "tag_group_memberships" ON "tag_group_memberships"."tag_id" = "tags"."id" INNER JOIN "tag_groups" ON "tag_groups"."id" = "tag_group_memberships"."tag_group_id" WHERE (tag_groups.id NOT IN (
        SELECT tag_group_id
        FROM tag_group_permissions
        WHERE group_id = 0))
